prompt.text: Collect the GPS coordinates of the registration site

Hello, my name is {{data.interviewer}}. I will collect some personal data about the current head of household and the household composition in order to register you in the XXX programme of the RCRC.

Do you have a few minutes ?
Could you please provide me with an identification document of the head of household?

hint.text: Note: Please verify that the respondent is a member of the household.  If he is not the head of household, he will have to show the identification document of the head of household. Now, reading the identification document of the head of household:

constraint_message.text: Please type LASTNAME in uppercase only.

hint.text: Must be 10 digits with no dashes or spaces

constraint_message.text: Please key in exactly the 10 digits of the phone number

prompt.text: 11. Number of adult males in HH
12. Number of adult females in HH
14. Total Number of people in HH (including HH representative).

hint.text: Must equal {{calculates.family_sum}} and at least one

constraint_message.text: The total number of people in HH is not correct. It should equal the total number of males, females and children

prompt.text: Do you consider your household being affected by the current disaster?
15. How do you consider the damage of your house?
16. How many people from your household do suffer from chronicle diseases (diabetes, high blood pressure, HIV, etc)?

hint.text: Must be less than or equal {{calculates.family_sum}}

constraint_message.text: This cannot exceed the total number of persons of the HH.

prompt.text: 17. How many people from your household are more than 75 years old?

hint.text: Must be less than or equal {{calculates.adult_sum}}

constraint_message.text: This cannot exceed the total number of persons of the HH.

prompt.text: 18. How many people from your household are disabled?

hint.text: Must be less than or equal {{calculates.family_sum}}

constraint_message.text: This cannot exceed the total number of persons of the HH.

prompt.text: 19. How many people from your household have been injured during the current disaster?

hint.text: Must be less than or equal {{calculates.family_sum}}

constraint_message.text: This cannot exceed the total number of persons of the HH.

prompt.text: 20. How many people from your household have been killed during the current disaster?

hint.text: Must be less than or equal {{calculates.minus_one}}

constraint_message.text: This cannot exceed the total number of persons of the HH minus one.

prompt.text:
You can now proceed to the printing desk where you will be provided with you RCRC beneficiary card. You will be informed soon about the details of the program.

In case of distribution,  please come with this RCRC beneficiary card and your {{data.id_type}} in order to verify your identity.

Thank you, the registration process has been completed!
